==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tropilidene
<hw>Tro*pil"i*dene</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Tropine</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A liquid hydrocarbon
obtained by the dry distillation of tropine with quicklime. It is
regarded as being homologous with dipropargyl.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

